{"tid":1802028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(Brainstorm) 「黃店通」可唔可行？","createTime":"2019-12-29T06:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T06:55:43.000Z","uid":65965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb39c28425c0b093e51e6b93f77d2df4737bc02f","tid":1802028,"uid":65965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"有「黃店通」前，首先我地要有一套明確且有公信力的黃店標準。<br />\n<br />\n比如：<br />\n1.店內不能播TVB<br />\n2.泛「反政府」、反支、支持本土<br />\n3.不強迫捐款，但有捐既一定有分加<br />\n4.主動拒絕藍絲、警曱及其家屬生意<br />\n5.安裝黃店通<br />\n（歡迎再加）<br />\n<br />\n目前主要既黃店都係消費、零售、服務性行業居多。<br />\n黃絲可以係黃店通增值（等同於八達通增值），再係黃店內等值消費時使用。<br />\n<br />\n入1000蚊黃店通，當黃店通收3%手續費（base大左可以下調）。<br />\n比如說個飯本身係賣40$ 黃店通價就會係41.2，所以就直接賣41.2黎cover左個價錢（1999）<br />\n<br />\n黃店可以係月結時搵返黃店通公司拎返等值現金。<br />\n手續費作營運成本用途。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以幫黃絲們養成真正到黃店消費既習慣，<br />\n而商戶可以有數據咁量化到有幾多生意係因黃店而來，<br />\n從而幫助其他人加入黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎討論，純9up"},{"pid":"0d7f6d31b1cba86fd507eb65c6427db80262fed7","tid":1802028,"uid":65965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6d9be6829566e0983f5735dbd2d2b0f4371e40","tid":1802028,"uid":84363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"技術上難唔難做"},{"pid":"a00da343a99ee066d2910f61f6004013f87cdcd8","tid":1802028,"uid":65965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6d9be6829566e0983f5735dbd2d2b0f4371e40","tid":1802028,"uid":84363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"技術上難唔難做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"唔知 有無it高手"},{"pid":"9922184fb99702ce618d2fb3cbaf5faf849bd9a7","tid":1802028,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"惡撚過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩黑社會埋堆收陀地"},{"pid":"b05439392971e8a4a750833e387b0704c95847ae","tid":1802028,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<del><span style=\"color: red;\">4.主動拒絕藍絲、警曱及其家屬生意</span></del><br />\n錯哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要做大個餅，錢係愈多愈好<br />\n<br />\n另外要明文宣揚<br />\n「鼓勵轉色，包容偽黃」「美心轉色照幫襯」<br />\n而唔係圍爐搞小圈子"},{"pid":"9b492c55d786a1dd4038bd22a56a99e4accb9cbe","tid":1802028,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得反唔反中 係後話 但要支持本土&gt;中"}]}